[Amit Varma]: Aditi, welcome to The Scene and The Unseen.

00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:33.000
[Unknown]: Hi! This is so incredibly exciting.

00:04:33.000 --> 00:04:36.000
[Amit Varma]: And not just Aditi, Abbas, welcome to The Scene and The Unseen as well.

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:40.000
[Guest 2]: Hi Amit, good to be on the show I produce once again.

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:43.000
[Amit Varma]: Yeah, good to be in front of the mic instead of behind it.

00:04:43.000 --> 00:04:45.000
[Amit Varma]: Right, welcome back.

00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:49.000
[Amit Varma]: So Aditi, we have this, and you're going to probably find this a little disconcerting,

00:04:49.000 --> 00:04:52.000
[Amit Varma]: but we've started this new custom on The Scene and The Unseen

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:57.000
[Amit Varma]: that before we get down to whatever the serious subject of the day is,

