01:08:32.320 --> 01:08:56.320
[Guest 1]: What makes me hopeful about stand up comedy also is the fact that it is such a low cost thing to start is I know that most of the rooms that are running right now were this guy going up to a restaurant owner and being like, Bhai sahab, bhai sahab, wo jaga hai na, jab log kha rahe hain, kuch bole kya mic pe. Restaurant's like, theek hai yaar. And that's how most comedy rooms start is while you're trying to eat food, someone's like, sir, what's the deal with airplane food?

01:08:56.320 --> 01:09:23.320
