[Guest 1]: May I say this? I love telling this bit, but one of my favorite stories about humor in times of duress was during in the concentration camps where they would have comedians, where the concentration camps prisoners would be sitting in front with the SS officers behind on chairs and a comedian would come and tell jokes.

01:10:19.320 --> 01:10:43.320
